### Test Status Endpoints

# Test 1: Get available status transitions for a user
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/user/1/status-transitions
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

# Test 2: Update user status to ACTIVE
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/updateOneUser
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

###

# Test 3: Update user status to REJECT with note
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/updateOneUser
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "status": "REJECT",
  "statusNote": "Documents incomplete - please provide additional verification"
}

###

# Test 4: Update user status to INACTIVE with note
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/updateOneUser
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "status": "INACTIVE",
  "statusNote": "Account temporarily suspended due to policy violation"
}

###

